# EXISTING STRUCTURES

# ERROR TIPS
### Errors when getting entities at specific positions
- Ensure that an entity of the specified type exists at the given position before attempting to retrieve it using `get_entity()`. Double-check the coordinates and the entity type.

### Errors when extracting items
- You can only extract items that exist in the target inventory. Before extracting, ensure that the item you are trying to extract is present in the inventory of the target entity.
